item.description:

[quote=“aquikzebra, post:2, topic:345470”]I was pretty surprised when i first found this out…

To add the models, firstly put them in the models folder in your client, secondly, log on ingame and say "add model (model id here) so ex:) add model 6832

The client will say “model 6832 added sucessfully”

So if your adding customs, add the ints and copile then it should work

To add the models, firstly put them in the models folder in your client, secondly, log on ingame and say "add model (model id here) so ex:) add model 6832
